%F A136580 a(n) = (-1)^n*exp(1)*Gamma(0, 1)/2 - Re(Gamma(0, -1))*exp(-1)/2 + (n+2)!*((-1)^n*Re(Gamma(-n-2, -1))*exp(-1)-Gamma(-n-2, 1)*exp(1))/2, where Gamma(a, x) is the upper incomplete Gamma function.
